These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: red, fuchsia, ebony, lilac, orange, brown
6 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog, mouse, rabbit
 1. the person who likes ebony is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##5
 3. the person who likes orange is not the owner of the mouse##6
 4. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 7. the owner of the mouse is not the person who likes fuchsia##6
 8. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who likes red is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the person who likes lilac##7
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
11. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
12. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the owner of the cat is the person who likes red##1
14. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
15. the person who likes brown is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Color   | lilac   | red | ebony   | brown     | fuchsia    | orange   |
| Pet           | mouse | cat   | rabbit | hedgehog | guinea-pig | goldfish |

