.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, drama, fantasy, horror, time-travel
City: paris, hannover, hamburg, boston, new-york, london
 1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 2. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 7. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching horror movies is not the person traveling to new-york##6
10. the person traveling to paris is somewhere between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to boston##7
11. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
13. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
14. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
15. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
16. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
17. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the person watching horror movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | time-travel | fantasy | horror     | drama      | disaster |
| City           | hannover         | hamburg        | new-york   | boston | paris | london    |

