.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, boat, skateboard, motorbike, train
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, lacrosse, parkour, surfing, swimming
 1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person driving the skateboard##6
 5. the person driving the van is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
10. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the snowmobile##7
11. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
13. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
14. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Transport   | motorbike        | skateboard | train    | van    | boat | snowmobile |
| Sport      | basketball | surfing  | swimming | parkour | baseball | lacrosse      |

