.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, water
There are 6 different favourite colors: fuchsia, brown, ebony, ivory, mauve, purple
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 2. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 3. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the person who likes brown is not the person drinking mirinda##6
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking mirinda##7
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking water##7
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking lemonade##7
10. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5
13. the person who likes ebony is the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | almond-milk | water | hot-chocolate | mirinda | 7up   |
| Color   | ebony  | ivory      | fuchsia | mauve     | purple | brown |

