.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-5::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, lemonade, 7up, cola, almond-milk
6 different pets are kept: cat, dog, ferret, goat, goldfish, pony
 1. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 2. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
 5. the person drinking cola is between the owner of the goldfish and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 6. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking milk##7
 9. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
10. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking sprite##1
12. the owner of the ferret is not the person drinking sprite##6
13. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
14. the owner of the ferret is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |  3   |     4     |     5      |   6    |
| Beverage   | milk | almond-milk | cola  | sprite | lemonade | 7up |
| Pet           | pony  | dog  | goat | goldfish  | ferret     | cat    |

