 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the bartender is on the left of the engineer##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is not the musician##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the engineer##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the doctor##1
 8. the dancer is on the right of the musician##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
10. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
11. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the paramedic and the doctor##7

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |     4     |    5     |     6      |
| Birthday   | july | december | march | november    | september | april |
| Job    | doctor  | musician   | dancer | bartender | engineer | paramedic  |

