 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
 6. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person eating tomato##7
 7. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
