10. the person who growsdaisy is in an even position##4
11. the colombian is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
12. the russian is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaisy##5
13. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese | indian   | colombian  | nigerian      | russian  |
| Flower         | amaryllis      | daisy | tulip | begonia | orchid | zinnia |

