.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-19::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, almond-milk, tea, milk, hot-chocolate
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, skateboard, train, tram, trike
 1. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
 3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 5. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 6. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking milk and the person driving the boat##2
 7. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 9. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
11. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person driving the tram is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the motorbike##7
13. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Beverage         | juice   | milk | lemonade      | tea | hot-chocolate  | almond-milk   |
| Transport   | train | trike  | motorbike | boat   | tram | skateboard |

