.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, prince, ritmeester, blend, dannemann, bongani
The people have 6 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, fisherman, journalist, project-manager, scientist
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 3. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
 4. the siglo-smoker is somewhere between the journalist and the dressmaker##7
 5. the scientist is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 6. the ritmeester-smoker is the project-manager##1
 7. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
 8. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
 9. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
10. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
11. the scientist is on the right of the fisherman##1
12. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
13. the prince-smoker is somewhere between the siglo-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##7
14. the dressmaker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
15. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Cigar   | ritmeester         | blend | prince | siglo   | bongani | dannemann  |
| Job     | project-manager | journalist  | fisherman  | scientist | dressmaker  | accountant |

 